section.p:
StatCounter uses two identifiers, a project ID and a security code.  You can find them in your Project Config under Settings.  Or the code provided will contain lines such as
            var sc_project=11538430;
            var sc_invisible=1;
            var sc_security="72e1390a";
        In which case you would use two command-line switches:
            -stringparam html.statcounter.project 11538430
            -stringparam html.statcounter.security 72e1390a
